Getcvar (script event)
======================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the string for a CVar.

Usage
-----

*string* getCVar( *string* **name** )

Parameters
----------

-   [name] - The name of the CVar.

Examples
--------

` `
`CVarValue = `<font color="#0000ff">`sys`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`getCVar`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#666666">`"g_showhud"`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script returns a string containing the value of the given CVar.


